(:action ExecuteCleanObject
    :parameters (?a - agent ?l - location ?r - receptacle ?ot - otype ?rt - rtype ?o - object)
    :precondition (and
        (cleansingProduct ?op)
        (holds ?a ?op)
        (atLocation ?a ?l)
        (receptacleAtLocation ?r ?l)
        (or (not (openable ?r)) (opened ?r))     
        (objectType ?o ?ot)
        (receptacleType ?r ?rt)
        
        (canContain ?rt ?ot)
        (inReceptacle ?o ?r)
        
        )
    :effect (and
        (not (hasSheds ?o))
        (clean ?o)
        (increase (total-cost) 4)
        )
 )

(:action WipeObject
    :parameters (?a - agent ?l - location ?o - object ?o2 - object ?r - receptacle)
    :precondition (and
            (dirty ?o)
            (wipingTargetType ?o ?t)
            (wipingAgentType ?o2 ?t)
            (atLocation ?a ?l)
            (receptacleAtLocation ?r ?l)
            (holds ?a ?o2)
            (inReceptacle ?o ?r)
            
            
            (or (not (openable ?r)) (opened ?r))  
            
        )
    :effect (and
                (not (dirty ?o))
                (increase (total-cost) 5)
            )
 )

(:action CoolObject
    :parameters (?a - agent ?l - location ?r - receptacle ?o - object)
    :precondition (and
            (coolable ?o)
            (or
                (receptacleType ?r RefrigeratorType SmallRefrigeratorType FreezerType)
                (and (receptacleType ?r SinkType) (objectType ?o Mugs))
            )
            (atLocation ?a ?l)
            (receptacleAtLocation ?r ?l)
            (inReceptacle ?o ?r)
            )
    :effect (and
                (increase (total-cost) 5)
                (cold ?o)
                (not (hot ?o))
            )
 )

(:action WaitFor
    :parameters (?a - agent ?l - location ?o - object ?r - receptacle ?t - timeOffset)
    :precondition
        (and
            (atLocation ?a ?l)
            (receptacleAtLocation ?r ?l)
            
            (inReceptacle ?o ?r)
        
            (heatable ?o)
            (isCool ?o)
        
        )
    :effect (and
                (isHot ?o)
                (not (isCool ?o))
                (increase (total-cost) (+ ?t 1))
            )
 )
